<br>
&lt;&lt;, but it's also somewhat more realistic.&gt;&gt;<br>
<br>
Dieing and going to your bind point is not realistic, consuming food without ever eating is not realistic, Zoning to escape a mob is not realistic, elevators in Gfay with no mechanism, no maintenance are not realistic. Realism is often overlooked because of game machanics, requirements. <br>
